Package: charitybrandequity
Title: Evidence-Based Comparison of Nonprofit Brand-Equity Architectures
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Gerald", "Czech", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Reproducible research compendium for a within-dataset comparison of
    three nonprofit brand-equity architectures (Faircloth 2005; Boenigk & Becker
    2016; Rios Romero et al. 2023) using CFA/SEM, with common-method, HTMT,
    ICC and measurement-invariance diagnostics.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.2)
Imports: here, dplyr, tidyr, tibble, purrr, readr, stringr, forcats,
    lavaan, semTools, psych, lme4, performance, gt, knitr, kableExtra,
    ggplot2, haven
